data.description: FHA Assumable Mortgage possible with this beautiful remodel on  this 3 bedroom, 2 Bath Hermitage home, the  perfect condo alternative! A must see! Recent complete Kitchen remodel, new cabinetry, granite counter tops, new flooring, overhead lighting, and appliances; all less than 2 years old! Primary Bedroom remodel, with walls, carpeting, overhead lighting and redone Master Bath, all within 2 years. The large Living Room boasts hardwood floors, fresh paint and revamped fireplace. Newer carpeting and paint in the 2 remaining Bedrooms.  New doors, landscaping, newer furnace and clean open basement add to the features. Basement appliances stay!   Fruit trees in the yard help add to privacy. Move right in, close to all the amenities in Hermitage!
